Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:46.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}その夢に届く未来で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:46.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}我会在那梦想成真的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:49.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}待っていて
